  "detailed_description": "Dive into the golden era of Japanese street racing. Choose from a list of iconic cars and perfect your driving skills in beautiful mountain roads. Challenge your friends and rivals in downhill or uphill battles.  At night, the streets are yours.<br><br><br>                                                                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608680/extras/8a69ca8263b9b7ee74312e602d8a58bf.poster.avif?t=1640805772\" width=580 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608680/extras/8a69ca8263b9b7ee74312e602d8a58bf.webm?t=1640805772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608680/extras/8a69ca8263b9b7ee74312e602d8a58bf.mp4?t=1640805772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Iconic cars</strong><br><br>In this arcade racing game choose from<br><br>14 iconic cars representing the spirit of golden era of street racing in mountain passes.<br><br><strong>Beautiful locations</strong><br><br>4 Beautiful locations with lots of layout options. Downhill or uphill, ring or open. <br>Drive on twisting roads to perfect your skills and challenge your friends in multiplayer races.<br><br><strong>Challenge your friends and rivals</strong><br><br>Up to 4 player multiplayer to race or drive around gorgeous mountain passes<br><br><br>                                                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608680/extras/becf0e0c504556cf4d7d4cb30c6e213f.poster.avif?t=1640805772\" width=580 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608680/extras/becf0e0c504556cf4d7d4cb30c6e213f.webm?t=1640805772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608680/extras/becf0e0c504556cf4d7d4cb30c6e213f.mp4?t=1640805772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
